import React from 'react' import Reactdom from 'react-dom' import { add, sub, div, mul } from "./App" Reactdom.render( <>
  1. Addition of two numbers are {add(3, 4)}
  2. Subtraction of two numbers are {sub(3, 4)}
  3. Multiplication of two numbers are {mul(3, 4)}
  4. Division of two numbers are {div(10, 3)}
, document.getElementById('root') )
